structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS

law.history: Repealed 1966 Ky. Acts ch. 172, sec. 91. -- Created 1960 Ky. Acts ch. 69, sec. 2, effective March 18, 1960.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Joint city-county powers; planning and zoning commission; board of zoning adjustment and appeals.
